    "reports/verification/2026-06-25/api_logs.txt": "2026-06-25 Dify API evidence excerpts\n=====================================\n\nConsole initialization issue observed:\n\n- Setup account failed\n- opendal.exceptions.PermissionDenied\n- path: privkeys/.../private.pem\n- Source: Permission denied (os error 13)\n\nResolution:\n\n- /app/api/storage ownership was corrected for the Dify API runtime user.\n- Storage write probe returned STORAGE_WRITE_PASS.\n- /console/api/setup later returned {\"step\":\"not_started\",\"setup_at\":null}, allowing setup to continue.\n\nPlugin and workflow evidence:\n\n- GET plugin_daemon management endpoints returned HTTP/1.1 200 OK.\n- POST plugin_daemon /dispatch/tool/validate_credentials returned HTTP/1.1 200 OK.\n- POST plugin_daemon /dispatch/tool/invoke returned HTTP/1.1 200 OK.\n- on_tool_execution logged Tool: db_query_extended.\n- Tool output included JSON rows from plugin_test_users with row_count=5.\n\nSource:\n\n- docker logs dify-api-1 --tail 120\n",
    "reports/verification/2026-06-25/README.md": "# 2026-06-25 Verification Evidence\n\nThis folder archives Phase 3 platform recovery and Dify Workflow validation evidence for `db_query_extended`.\n\nHuman-readable explanation: `reports/documentation/Phase3_Platform_Integration/2026-06-25/`.\n\n## Files\n\n- `workflow_mysql_result.json` — MySQL Dify Workflow API result evidence.\n- `workflow_postgresql_result.json` — PostgreSQL Dify Workflow UI validation record.\n- `plugin_daemon_logs.txt` — plugin-daemon recovery, installation, credential validation, and invoke log excerpts.\n- `api_logs.txt` — Dify API setup and workflow log excerpts.\n- `verify_plugin_output.txt` — final `verify_plugin.ps1` output.\n- `final_verification_matrix.md` — final MySQL/PostgreSQL verification matrix.\n- `error_password_result.md` — wrong-password error-path verification.\n\n## Screenshot Status\n\nNo local screenshot files were found in the project workspace for this validation round. UI validation is therefore tracked through API output, Dify API logs, plugin-daemon logs, and the manual validation notes above.\n",
    "reports/verification/2026-06-25/verify_plugin_output.txt": "[Phase2] Running db_query_extended plugin verification matrix...\n[Phase2] Verification report written to .\\verification\\phase2_verification_report.json\n\npass : 57\nfail : 0\nskip : 0\n\n[Phase2] PASS\n\nWorkflow evidence:\n\n- target: dify_workflow\n- case: workflow_api_call\n- status: PASS\n- workflow status: succeeded\n- total_steps: 3\n- outputs.result[0].row_count: 5\n- outputs.result[0].truncated: false\n",
